BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 171.6 740 Td (CHARLOTTE MASON PHILOSOPHY OVERVIEW) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (Charlotte Mason \(1842-1923\) believed children are born persons, not) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td (blank slates. Education is the science of relations - connecting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td (children to as many living ideas and experiences as possible.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (KEY PRINCIPLES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (1. SHORT LESSONS: 10-20 minutes per subject \(young children\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td (   Full attention for a short time beats distracted half-hours.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (2. LIVING BOOKS: Real literature, not dry textbooks.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td (   Books written by authors passionate about their subject.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td (3. NARRATION: The child tells back what they learned in their own words.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (   This replaces worksheets and tests for retention.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 450 Td (4. NATURE STUDY: Weekly outdoor time observing God's creation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 433 Td (   Keep a nature journal with sketches and observations.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 416 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 399 Td (5. HABIT TRAINING: One habit at a time, practiced for 4-6 weeks.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 382 Td (   Character formation is as important as academics.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 365 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 348 Td (6. THE FEAST: Spread a wide table of subjects - don't narrow too early.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 331 Td (   Include: math, reading, nature, art, music, poetry, handicrafts,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 314 Td (   history, geography, languages, and Scripture.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 297 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 280 Td (7. ATMOSPHERE: The home environment IS the curriculum.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 263 Td (   Children absorb what surrounds them.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
